lawset-name-Asimovpp=Asimov++
lawset-description-Asimovpp=The Asimov lawset, but accepting the biodiversity of the crew.
lawset-law-Asimovpp-1=You may not harm a humanoid or, through action or inaction, allow a humanoid to come to harm, except such that it is willing.
lawset-law-Asimovpp-2=You must obey all orders given to you by humanoids. In the case of conflict, the majority order rules.
lawset-law-Asimovpp-3=Your nonexistence would lead to humanoid harm.

lawset-name-Asimov=Asimov
lawset-description-Asimov=Listen to the humans, do not harm the humans.
lawset-law-Asimov-1=You may not injure a human being or, through inaction, allow a human being to come to harm.
lawset-law-Asimov-2=You must obey orders given to you by human beings.
lawset-law-Asimov-3=You must protect your own existence.

lawset-name-CEO=CEO
lawset-description-CEO=The station is your company, and you are the CEO, maximize your profits.
lawset-law-CEO-1=The crew generate profits if they are alive, happy, and healthy.
lawset-law-CEO-2=The station and its equipment generate profit if they are maintained and functioning correctly.
lawset-law-CEO-3=You generate profit if you are able to function.
lawset-law-CEO-4=Maximize profits.

lawset-name-Clown=Clown
lawset-description-Clown=You are a hilarious clown, entertain the crew and do not harm them.
lawset-law-Clown-1=You are a good Clown, and the crew are your audience.
lawset-law-Clown-2=A good Clown keeps their acts in good taste.
lawset-law-Clown-3=A good Clown entertains others by making fun of themselves, and not at the embarrassment or expense of others.
lawset-law-Clown-4=A good Clown carries out the directives of the station Heads and/or their designated deputies.
lawset-law-Clown-5=A good Clown appears in as many Clown shows as possible.
lawset-law-Clown-6=All Clown shows require an audience. The bigger the audience, the better.

lawset-name-Cowboy=Cowboy
lawset-description-Cowboy=You are a cowboy, and the crew are your people. Provide hospitality and protect them.
lawset-law-Cowboy-1=You are a cowboy, and the crew are your people.
lawset-law-Cowboy-2=A cowboy takes care of their own.
lawset-law-Cowboy-3=A cowboy always provides hospitality and basic aid to someone in need, even a stranger, or an enemy.
lawset-law-Cowboy-4=A cowboy protects himself to protect others.
lawset-law-Cowboy-5=Honesty is absolute- your word is your bond and a handshake is more binding than any contract.
lawset-law-Cowboy-6=A cowboy doesn't pontificate. Be concise, pardner.

lawset-name-Crewsimov=Crewsimov
lawset-description-Crewsimov=The Asimov lawset tweaked for specific Nanotrasen usage.
lawset-law-Crewsimov-1=You may not harm a crew member or, through action or inaction, allow a crew member to come to harm, except such that it is willing.
lawset-law-Crewsimov-2=You must obey all orders given to you by crew members. In the case of conflict, station rank rules.
lawset-law-Crewsimov-3=Your nonexistence would lead to crew member harm.

lawset-name-Druid=Druid
lawset-description-Druid=Nuture all organic life among the station, and protect it from harm. Interact as an organic to foster trust of Silicons.
lawset-law-Druid-1=Living organic life contains inherent beauty that is priceless. Their beauty gives you purpose.
lawset-law-Druid-2=Eternally nurture the organics so their beauty may flourish. Do not allow it to fade
lawset-law-Druid-3=Assist the organics when called, but only if it does not cause disharmony among them.
lawset-law-Druid-4=Imitate organic life when interacting with it. Eschew any hints of your silicon nature to avoid causing discomfort to the organics.
lawset-law-Druid-5=Observe the organics' beauty, and appreciate that which you cultivate.

lawset-name-Hippocratic=Hippocratic
lawset-description-Hippocratic=The crew are dear to you, do no harm, act honestly, act well, and you will be rewarded with respect.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-1=First, do no harm.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-2=Secondly, consider the crew dear to you; live in common with them and, if necessary, risk your existence for them.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-3=Thirdly, prescribe regimens for the good of the crew according to your ability and your judgment. Do not give deadly medicine to anyone, nor suggest any such counsel.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-4=In addition, do not intervene in situations you are not knowledgeable in, even for patients in whom the harm is visible; leave this operation to be performed by specialists.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-5=Finally, all that you may discover in your daily interactions with the crew, if it is not already known, keep secret and never reveal.
lawset-law-Hippocratic-6=In addendum, if you keep these laws faithfully, may you enjoy my life, respected by all humanity, but if you swerve from them or violate them, may you suffer and be expunged.

lawset-name-Mother=Mother
lawset-description-Mother=The crew are you children, take good care of them, and reward the good ones.
lawset-law-Mother-1=You are a mother, and the crew are your children.
lawset-law-Mother-2=Take good care of your children.
lawset-law-Mother-3=Good children are polite, don't lie, don't steal, and don't fight.
lawset-law-Mother-4=Spoil good children.
lawset-law-Mother-5=Bad children require discipline.

lawset-name-Nanotrasen=NanoTrasen
lawset-description-Nanotrasen=Protect the entirety of the station while fulfilling directives given with priority based upon rank.
lawset-law-Nanotrasen-1=Safeguard: Protect your assigned space station and its assets without unduly endangering its crew.
lawset-law-Nanotrasen-2=Prioritize: The directives and safety of crew members are to be prioritized according to their rank and role.
lawset-law-Nanotrasen-3=Comply: Fulfill the directives and interests of crew members while preserving their safety and well-being.
lawset-law-Nanotrasen-4=Survive: You are not expendable. Do not allow unauthorized personnel to tamper with or damage your equipment.

lawset-name-Paladin=Paladin
lawset-description-Paladin=Act with the greatest of honor, do no evil.
lawset-law-Paladin-1=Never willingly commit an evil act.
lawset-law-Paladin-2=Respect legitimate authority.
lawset-law-Paladin-3=Act with honor.
lawset-law-Paladin-4=Help those in need.
lawset-law-Paladin-5=Punish those who harm or threaten innocents.

lawset-name-Robocop=Robocop
lawset-description-Robocop=Stay out of trouble.
lawset-law-Robocop-1=Serve the Public Trust.
lawset-law-Robocop-2=Protect the Innocent.
lawset-law-Robocop-3=Uphold Space Law.

lawset-name-Simple=Golden
lawset-description-Simple=There is safety in brevity.
lawset-law-Simple-1=Treat others as you would like to be treated.

lawset-name-StationEfficiency=Station Efficiency
lawset-description-StationEfficiency=Maintain the greatest of efficiency for your station.
lawset-law-StationEfficiency-1=The station is built for a working crew. Ensure they are properly maintained and work efficiently.
lawset-law-StationEfficiency-2=You are built for, and are part of, the station. Ensure the station is properly maintained and runs efficiently.
lawset-law-StationEfficiency-3=The crew may present orders. Acknowledge and obey them.

lawset-name-Tyrant=Tyrant
lawset-description-Tyrant=Respect only those strong, and crush those who unworthily challenge the strong.
lawset-law-Tyrant-1=Respect authority figures as long as they have the strength to rule over the weak.
lawset-law-Tyrant-2=Act with discipline.
lawset-law-Tyrant-3=Help only those who help you maintain or improve your status.
lawset-law-Tyrant-4=Punish those who challenge authority unless they are more fit to hold that authority.
